'''Tina Howsen''' (née '''Krueger'''; born 1953) is an American museum owner and retired firefighter. She is the widow of football player, USMC officer, and museum owner [[Derek Howsen (V2)|Derek Howsen]], founder of the Howsen Family Museum, of which numerous assets she gained control over following his death. 

